      "role": "user",
      "content": "they were everything. they were my pulse. now there's just this... hollow thing where i used to be. it's like the person who made that art died, and now i'm just stuck with the remains. how am i supposed to keep going when there's nothing actually \"in here\" anymore? it feels so pointless to just exist for the sake of it.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
